import { MaterialModule } from './../../../shared/material.module'; import { AuthService } from './../../../shared/services/auth/auth.service'; import { AuthRoutingModule } from './../../auth-routing.module'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Router, RouterModule, Routes,ActivatedRoute } from '@angular/router'; @Component({ selector: 'app-login', templateUrl: './login.component.html', styleUrls: ['./login.component.sass'], }) export class LoginComponent implements OnInit { hide = true; constructor( private router:Router, route:AuthRoutingModule, private authService: AuthService, materialModule:MaterialModule ) { } ngOnInit(): void { if(false) { this.router.navigate(['auth/signup']); } } }
